- âœ… Automated compliance checking
- **âœ… Multi-phase workflow execution (Repository â†’ Planning â†’ Security â†’ Optimization â†’ Code Generation â†’ Deployment)**

### Security & IAM Management
- âœ… Root credential usage only for initial setup
